!name Classic guacamole
!author Tavin Turner
!date 06/19/2024

> fmt '%quantity %adj %ingredient'
> remainder 'remaining %ingredient'

-[prep] To prepare:
    - Medium dice [@avocado#2ct(medium, ripe):avo->fmt @tomato#1ct(roma):tomato->fmt]
    - Small dice @shallot#1/2ct:shallot->fmt
    ~ Slice @serrano#1-2ct|@jalapeno|@habanero#1ct:pepper->fmt
    - Juice @lime#1ct(medium, soft):lime_juice->fmt
-[mash] Mash :avo/[@salt#pinch :lime_juice#splash] => :mash_avo
-[mixin] Add [:tomato :shallot :pepper :lime#rest->remainder] => :plain_guac
-[season] Season :plain_guac/[@salt @pepper @cumin @coriander]
= Serve with chips, rice, or anything you like!